1 : the urban-rural threshold

The  proposal  for  the  site  is  to  create  an  exchange  between  the 
rural  workers  and  urban  inhabitants  by  creating  a  new  village 
centered  on  new  forms  of  high  density  agricultural  production. 
Sustainable  farming  of  food,  energy,  clean  water  and  air  is 
proposed  along  the  greenbelt  creating  a  productive  space  that 
bleeds  into  the site.  New  forms of  farming and education provide 
a venue  for migrant workers  to  increase  their skill set allowing  for 
urbanization and exchange. 

 
