5 : axis


The  excavation  of 
the  historic  north-south  axis  and 
the 
repurposing  of  several  existing  buildings  along  it  re-establishes 
a  public  way  that  becomes  the  central  armature  for  the  local 
community,  containing  a  library,  school,  health  care  facilities, 
shops  and  restaurants.  A  series  of  fountains  emphasize  the 
aesthetic  and  productive  value  of  water  along  the  main  axis, 
distributed  from  a  high-rise water  tower  at  the  top  of  the  axis  to 
the rooftop farms via the aqueduct. 

